{"type": "article", "id": 12507, "title": "可收纳书的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-23T07:53:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141157hZFrbYDwtNqJROzX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLukas Avena 的这一款椅子专门为喜欢读书读报的人设计，都市年轻人常常没有足够大起居空间，便经常会遇到没看完的书或是报纸没地方放的问题。这款椅子把普通的扶手变成了倾斜的形状，看起来就像一个报架，虽然不能储存大量的书籍，但是把正在阅读的书籍搭在上面，既节省存储空间，又方便继续阅读。这是<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/lukasave\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140240Y3UpAbMXL96TuDy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140240MGKuhZfQ3c64UHD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140242lnWLxD1kB5wjzcEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140243AirBwlgQHahmnpxs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402437mu91hKgtaiyrN8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}